      <scopecontent id="aspace_c4bc46545d25c78bd44213f0c216c363">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The papers consist of reports, minutes of meetings, correspondence, printed matter and other papers largely related to the American Public Health Association and particularly its Committee for the Creation of a Medical Care Section. These papers form part of the Contemporary Medical Care and Health Policy Collection.</p>  
